data.title: French President Emile Loubet 1900 Engraved Invitation, King of Spain in Paris
data.meta_description: This is an engraved invitation/RSVP card from French President Emile Loubet and his wife, for a lunch with the King of Spain in Paris. It has Loubet's monogram at the top-left. DATE: Circa 1900.
